GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{appId}}/positions/all
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 新建应用职位
# @name createPos
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{appId}}/positions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

